        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Rumor has it that... he wasn\\'t just your average awakened machine, though I don\\'t have details on what made him special. Still, it wouldn\\'t surprise me if he was the one manipulating Aleksei.', 4: '1'}"
    },
